        %meta{:name => "twitter:image", :content => "#{meta.twitterimage}"}

%article#feature-article
    %div.container
        %div.row
            %div.twelve.columns#header
                %div.left_spacing
                    %h5
                        <a href="#"><span style="margin-right: 4%">Home</span><a href="#determinants-chart"><span style="margin-right: 4%">Determinants</span></a><a href="#use_jump"><span style="margin-right: 4%">Uses</span><a><a href="#contacts"><span style="margin-right: 4%">Contact</span></a>
        %div#header_image
            %h5.row.left_spacing
                DETERMINANTS
            %h5.row.left_spacing
                OF HEALTH

        %div#problem_statement
            %div.left_spacing.right_spacing
                %p.emphasize_text
                    PROBLEM
                %hr
                %p
                    Current health systems focus is on clinical care. However, it is necessary to view health as a holistic measure of an individual's entire living situation and life experience. These factors that strongly affect an individuals overall quality of health are the <span style="font-weight: bold">determinants of health</span>.
                %p
                    Extending far beyond medical care, these factors can be used to improve health within the clinical, population, and public health spaces.

        %div#determinants-chart-wrapper.left_spacing.right_spacing
            %div.determinants-chart
